data.title: Sebastian Kehl stats and ratings
data.meta_description: Sebastian Kehl profile player page. Goals, matches, stats, player ratings and more.
data.text:
If Sebastian Kehl is going to be in TuS Röllbach lineup, it will be confirmed on Sofascore one hour before the match starts.

If Sebastian Kehl plays you will also be able to follow his live Sofascore rating, statistics and heatmap. Sebastian Kehl football player profile displays all matches and competitions with statistics for all the matches Sebastian Kehl played in. Most important stats for each competition, including average Sofascore rating, matches played, goals, assists, cards and other relevant data are also displayed.
